text: First year antaragni ke liye practice kar rahe the tab laga tha acads ka pressure aane pe sabse pehle aakarsh katega :p I'm glad ki I was proved wrong, kyuki tere sense of humour aur jokes ke bina practice ki lambi raatein itni yadgaar aur mazedar nahi hoti aur na hi itna accha dost milta jiske sath baitho toh hamesha hasi hi aayi. Mumbai aayega (hopefully) toh milenge aur is baar sath mein piyenge bc
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text:
Yoo sabse 'tight' senior :p Tere sath reh kar, raat raat bhar nachne, first year me sath holi khelne, practice me ga*nd marwane aur itni sari parties karke bohot maza aaya. Mujhe yaad hai kaise tune bola tha ki tu soch ke aaya hai ki college me aake dance karunga, aur kya dance kiya hai bhai ! Sorry for all the 'mom' jokes I've made at your expense xD Campus me aakhri baar milna reh gaya apna :( Aise hi 'tight' dance karte rehna aur har jagah chaapte rehna. Waiting to meet you again soon, kisaan <3

PS : 1st year galaxy dance drama wala video dekh ke aaj bhi hasi aa jati hai :p
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text: technical guruji _/\_, gamer supreme. Kisi bhi situation me cool rehke samajhdari se kaam karna koi aap se sikhe. In aakhri kuch dino mein sath me movies dekh aur party kar bohot maza aaya. Aage bhi milte rahenge apan aur maze karenge.
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text:
"Oye guru balle balle !!" ye har jagah bol bol kar bohot sataya tha tujhe first year me ye aaj bhi yaad hai xD. Sath me resident evil khelte waqt kaise ek dusre ko darate the or kaise apni phat jati thi ye yaad karke aaj bhi hasi aa jati hai. Chaapu or gyaani toh tu tha hi shuru se aur bohot gyaan bhi pelta tha sabko even though kisi ko sunna nahi tha :p Isi tarah chaapte rehna paaji lekin yaar sath me ek baar campus me milke party karni reh gayi :(
Milke is kami ko bhi poora karna hai jald hi. touch me rehna bhai.

PS : yaha bio mein bhi chaap hi diya hai, tension na le :p
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text: Sapole !! First year antaragni mein mile the tab se ye naam dimag mein hai par kisne rakha tha yaad nahi xD Practice ke time itni sari bakchodiya ki aur woh qualify karne ke baad dance room wala celebration, ye toh hamesha yaad rahega. Aage life mein chaapte rehna aur snaps bhejte rehna <3

text: Tera jitna passion dekha hi nahi kisime dance ka. Freshers se jo ye dosti rahi hai woh hamesha bani rahegi, itni sari memories hai aur panda se sabse zyada galiya shayad hum dono ne hi khayi hai xD Very lucky to have a friend like you jo itna saaf dil ka ho, jisne hamesha sath diya aur encourage kiya. Umeed hai jald milne ko milega bhai, bas agli baar mile tab maarna mat :p

text: Dance, acads, laundiyabazi, darubazi sabme expert hai apna Gandhi xD Har cheez ko itna mast manage kar usme chaapna koi tujhse better shayad hi kar sakta hai. Placement ke waqt itni help karne ka shukriya aur rahi baat sath peene ki toh woh bhi pura kar lenge agli mulakat mein
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text: Freshers mein mile the tabse galiya hi khayi hai panda ki xD sath baith ke tinder pe fake ids banayi aur seniors ke maze liye the inter iit ke waqt ye bhi yaad hai. Baadme baatein shayad kum ho gayi ho lekin dosti toh hamesha hi kayam rahegi, toh milte rehna fellow bboy <3
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text:
Yoo gotyaa !! 
Still remember that one time in first year when you didn't know Hindi and innocently asked for a "bhosdi" xD. Your Hindi has obviously improved since then, not so sure about that wish though :p Thank you for incessantly pestering me to try out new 'stuff' all these years and thank you for introducing me to a whole new dimension of music and movies. Always loved and have been in awe of your artistic abilities and I hope we get to meet soon when you come for your Masters in Mumbai. All the best, stay in touch and keep sending the movie recommendations <3. 

Also, an obligatory Mohan Lal ki mkb :p
author: Aditya Abhaykirti Paikrao

text: "yahi baatein toh baad me yaad ayengi". Yaad toh rahega bro kaise har party me sabko pareshan karke khud maze karta tha, sumukh ko chhedta tha aur rota bhi tha xD. Gaaliyan bohot khayi hai tune hum se (deserve bhi karta tha :p) par masti bhi utni hi ki hai sath me. Tereko jaate waqt uthana bhool gaya uske liye sorry bro. text:
"A reserved guy who mostly kept to himself and spent most of his time either engrossed in his phone or sleeping. In short - chutiya" 
This was my first impression of you when I walked into D-105. But like they say, appearances are often deceptive. Jitna chutiya samjha tha usse kai guna zyada bakchod aur accha dost nikla tu. Bohot sari memories hain tere sath bhai. "bhabi maa saman" wala joke jo humare darwaze pe likha tha, har baar sath canteen jana, sath khana order karna, summers me sath cooler lena, raat ko baith kar chutiyon wali baate karna aur pata nahi kitni sari yaadein hain. Mil kar Sath party karte aur yaad karte yeh sare pal, par tu saale campus aaya nahi ðŸ˜ . Chalo phir baki toh tera set hai hi sab, bas shaadi me bula zaroor lena :p teri gpl bhi leni hai sabko. bohot sara pyaar <3

text:
Honestly, I don't think any amount of words could possibly articulate the bond we share. You have been an integral and a steadfast part of my IITK journey, for which you have my utmost gratitude. From being the first friend I made here, teaching me a night before MTH101 midsem, dancing together at so many occasions to getting drunk and rolling on quad ki grass and many more bakchodiya, I have cherished every beautiful memory we have made along the way. You are definitely one of the dearest and closest friends I have made here. Bas ab aur zyada nahi likha jaa raha xD aur haan milne toh tu aa hi raha day1 wali ((job)) lekar toh tab milke aur bakchodi karenge :p

Also, eagerly waiting for the D-bot reunion at your destination wedding (@Community Centre, IITK)
